Usage : setmout <message>
Restricted to immortals only.

Set your exit message.  The message given is to the room when you exit.
In <message>, $N and $T must appear.  $N represents your name and $T represents
the direction you leave to.

KEEP YOUR ENTRY/EXIT MESSAGES IN THEME WITH Forgotten Realms!

Examples:

setmout $N gets bored and leaves $T.
setmout You hear a loud noise and suddenly $N turns and flees $T.

See also:
setmin, setmmout, setmmin, review
